-*- mode: org -*-

* --gateway
* cli
* --count
how many pings
* --all or --any or --half
By default, returns success if ANY ips are reachable.  --all switches to only
if all are reachable.  --half if at least half of the pings get a response.
* --quiet, --verbose
normal output should display all the ping output, verbose has extra debug,
quiet is silent
